name: World of Skins
description:
IF you are a Minecraft Player and looking for the best app to search for your new Best Skins, "World of Skins for Minecraft PE" is the perfect app to grab.

Go ahead and give it a try! You will be surprised with the quality of skins we have hand-prepared for you.

Notice: "World of Skins for Minecraft PE" is not affiliated with the game 'Minecraft' or its creator Mojang AB. "World Of Skins for Minecraft PE" is only an aid tool for the game, 'Minecraft'.
